e more general case of random unitary channels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 Feb 2008 23:51:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 16 Feb 2008 15:55:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
